HEADWORD: Obiter
<hw>Ob"i*ter</hw> <pr>(⟦ocr⟧b"⟦icr⟧*t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<ety>[L., on the way; <ets>ob</ets> (see <er>Ob-</er>) + <ets>iter</ets>
a going, a walk, way.]</ety> <def>In passing; incidentally; by the
